{"tid":1916861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終極手足裝備詳解：濾罐篇 （重要裝備po ！)","createTime":"2020-03-09T06:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T16:33:48.000Z","uid":344033,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6e80f5705425e82dd67c6eb03203f5002511fb","tid":1916861,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">終極手足裝備詳解：濾罐篇 （重要裝備po )</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終極手足裝備詳解：防毒面具篇</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913336</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(睇左依個先睇罐！）</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講完防毒面具，依家講<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">濾罐</span></span>，濾罐主要分為兩種，一種係40mm 濾罐，適用於大部分軍用防毒面具，3M full face 加parts 亦可用；另一種係bayonet，例如3M 濾罐、honeywell 罐。<br />\n<br />\n40mm 罐最大好處就係大部分都係NBC filter，預左比人打生化戰，所以多數乜都防倒，就算係工業用嘅都擋到山埃，防護力幾高，但係相對3M 罐黎講比較難買，亦都<span style=\"color: red;\">偏重</span>，例如根據網上資料，7093 大概 45g，而Scott Pro 2000 就大概 265g。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2a3GP1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2a3GP1.jpg&h=7fc90ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozUW1Qf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozUW1Qf.png&h=73006d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上一般<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 40mm CBRN</span></span> 罐已經夠曬，military surplus 一般唔貴，百幾二百已經有，例如FP-5 filter 都係$200 度，不過部分過左期，不過正常黎講密封包裝嘅過左期幾年都用得。如果擔心品質問題嘅，可以考慮買民用NBC filter，或者工業用 ABEK2P3 filter，例如 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Scott Pro 2000 系列或者 Mestel Multipurpose 40mm</span></span>，之前見過carousel 有人賣，不過貴外國網一二百左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMLrEB3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMLrEB3.jpg&h=ad201f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於bayonet 今次主力講番 3M，因為喺香港最容易買到。3M 罐分兩種，一種輕便版一次過濾曬氣體同粒子，例如60926，另一種就只有單一功能，一係濾氣體，一係就粒子，例如6006、7093。要擋TG ，必須氣體同粒子都擋，齋擋氣體淨係隔到味，隔唔到TG粒子，齋擋粒子就隔唔到味。<br />\n<br />\n就住過濾山埃黎講，6099 頂到最耐，喺1000 ppm 濃度之下，頂到大概350 分鐘，而6006 只頂到90 分鐘倒，根據明報，發射催淚彈現場山埃濃度大概30 ppm，理論上兩款喺現場應該都可以頂得住，手足們可以自行考慮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhmyjBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhmyjBB.jpg&h=d6be7a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n60926 依種一舊過嘅罐其中一個缺點就係因為要一舊過放曬擋氣體嘅6006罐 同擋粒子嘅P100 棉，罐入面地方有限，所以裡面擋粒子嘅P100棉壽命係入面6006 嘅一半，所以基本上用到「一半」就要換。<br />\n常見嘅濾罐組合如下：<br />\n6099<br />\n60926 <br />\n7093/6035 +6006 <br />\n2097+6006<br />\n2091+6006<br />\n<br />\n其中7093、6035 有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">防水</span></span>功能，適合救火隊同企較前嘅手足，棉量係一般嘅雙倍份量，壽命較長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rW4zOvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrW4zOvz.jpg&h=f07c9e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有手足問點樣先知要換罐</span></span>，簡單講，6006等擋氣體嘅罐方面，如果你聞到味咁就要換，至於擋粒子嘅P100 棉，用到呼吸阻力好大就要換，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">有手足計過6092X 系列壽命大概 如下<br />\n高濃度：200mins <br />\n開放環境 100hrs <br />\n密閉場所 30hrs </span></span><br />\n不過依家有埋山埃，實際情況自行考慮。"},{"pid":"de3343c3d6544504aeded0a8c9acf1d3adb41f0e","tid":1916861,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9af66736d14dbb6522ae8ecc2145f8ee8f6d5e90","tid":1916861,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"高汁"},{"pid":"e9212ccf54ab2fdfca401859b1c85875a9991aba","tid":1916861,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"123bf762bcdc32bfae4ce36a6db53cd716ce1304","tid":1916861,"uid":20442,"lik